data.description: Freshly renovated condo in the heart of Lauderhill located within the Environ community. Enjoy your coffee and the views on your large balcony overlooking the beautiful golf course. The redone kitchen is bright and features stainless steel appliances, a bar area, ample counter and storage space and really ties the home together. Property features restricted entrance to the building (code access) tennis court golf and more. Amenities include bowling pickel ball gym yoga movie theater dance hall and basketball courts
